	Financial Professionals-Compliance : Cape Securities


































































Financial Professionals-Compliance















Financialprofessionals












The demands of an ever-changing marketplace

          Cape’s Compliance Team is here to bring you new ways to help clients reach their goals while staying in line with their risk guidelines. With professional and productive attention, we help our advisors stay up-to-date with compliant solutions and processes.
        

          In an industry that’s constantly evolving, ensuring compliance is vital to your business continuity. One lapse can be detrimental – something you and your firm cannot afford. The last thing you want is to learn of errors from your clients or from regulators. That’s where Cape’s regulatory expertise enters the picture – to help you avoid the risk of noncompliance and understand the latest compliance best-practices.
        















































	Business-Insurance : Cape Securities


































































Business-Insurance















Businesses
        














Diverse products for multifaceted protection
        
Insurance is central to wealth management. As complex and diverse as investing, it equally requires specialized knowledge. We provide our advisors with expert advice and our clients with attractive products through our insurance agency, Cape Insurance Solutions, Inc.
        
Our comprehensive suite of products and technology, partnered with some of the highest payouts in the industry, creates a program that adds value to our advisors’ insurance business. Services include:
        

Property & Casualty
Life and Health
Indexed and fixed annuities

If you’re a client interested in exploring life or health insurance solutions, finding suitable protection for your home or vehicle, or considering various types of annuities (individual and joint) and plans for retirement, contact your nearest Cape advisor to help you locate and learn all about the products you need.
        
















































