Cape Securities Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























cape securities inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Cape Securities, Inc. operates as a brokerage firm. The Company offers traditional stocks, bonds, and mutual funds to investors, as well as direct participation programs, unit investment trusts, and Reg-D investments for accredited investors and corporations. Cape Securities serves clients in the United States.




